description: Forward CTF4 primer with A adaptamer. For ORF cloning.
Reverse CTF4 primer with B adaptamer. For ORF cloning.
Forward CTF4 primer roughly 300 bp upstream of ORF. For mutagenesis integration.
Forward CTF4 primer with A adaptamer and homology to a FLAG epitope tag. For N-terminal FLAG tagging Ctf4
Forward CTF4 primer with FLAG epitope tag and homology to CTF4. For N-terminal FLAG tagging Ctf4
Forward CTF4 primer to introduce N-terminal FLAG epitope with A homology for cloning.
Reverse CTF4 primer to introduce C-terminal FLAG epitope with A homology for cloning.
Reverse CTF4 primer roughly 300 bp upstream of ORF. For mutagenesis integration.
Forward CTF4 primer with A adaptamer. For N-terminal FLAG epitope tagging of ORF
Reverse CTF4 primer with B adaptamer. For C-terminal FLAG epitope tag.

CTF4 C-terminal deletion of all residues beginning at AA position 783. Removes alpha 1-6 helices which comprise the primary binding site for Pol1 and Sld5. Contains stop codon and B homology for cloning into e.g. pWJ1781

CTF4 C-terminal deletion of all residues beginning at AA position 490. Removes alpha 1-6 helices which comprise the primary binding site for Pol1 and Sld5 and WD repeats 1-6 which comprise a trimerization domain. Contains stop codon and B homology for cloning into e.g. pWJ1781
CTF4 C-terminal deletion of all residues beginnina at AA position 411. Removes alpha 1-6 helices WD repeats and two checkpoing dependent phosphosites. Contains stop codon and B homology

CTF4 N-terminal truncation of predicted NLS region. Contains start codon and A homology sequence for cloning into e.g. pWJ1781. NLS at AA 11-41 prediced by http://nls-mapper.iab.keio.ac.jp/cgi-bin/NLS_Mapper_y.cgi
CTF4 N-terminal truncation of predicted NLS region. Re-introduces a Myc NLS sequence (PAAKRVKLD PMID:26011555). Contains a start codon and A homology sequence for cloning into e.g. pWJ1781.

CTF4 N-terminal truncation of first 402 AA with Myc-NLS (PAAKRVKLD PMID:26011555) start codon and A homology sequence for cloning into e.g. pWJ1781. Only contains C-terminal Rad53/Mec1 dependent phospho-sites WD repeats and alpha-helices with NLS

CTF4 N-terminal truncation of first 464 AA with Myc-NLS (PAAKRVKLD PMID:26011555) start codon and A homology sequence for cloning into e.g. pWJ1781. Only contains C-terminal WD repeats and alpha-helices with NLS
CTF4 N-terminal truncation of first 776 AA with Myc-NLS (PAAKRVKLD PMID:26011555) start codon and A homology sequence for cloning into e.g. pWJ1781. Only contains C-terminal alpha-helices with NLS
